snippet.title: "TELL ME" Release STREAM!
snippet.description:
If you like this stream and want to tip you can do so by going to my paypal via:
http://paypal.me/jacobkoopmanofficial
or 
https://streamelements.com/jacobkoopmanmusic/tip

My latest Song is now out! have a listen now on spotify: 
https://open.spotify.com/track/1YNidBZDduVlIP4eiV2NFA?si=SecwKLWyQd22pvhWIoMu-g

**I ALSO STREAM ON TWITCH!**
http://twitch.tv/jakumaru
follow me:
INSTAGRAM: http://instagram.com/jakumaru
FACEBOOK: http://facebook.com/jacobpkoopman



Thanks to the massive support from my Patrons for making this happen! Erika Berglund
